<Layout title="About Hummingbird Social Studio | Wedding Template Design Studio" description="Learn about Hummingbird Social Studio, a wedding template design studio creating editable invitations, wedding suites, and printable stationery.">
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero"><div class="container content"><p class="eyebrow">About the studio</p><h1>Thoughtful wedding templates with a warm, modern feel.</h1><p class="lead">Hummingbird Social Studio was created for couples, hosts, and planners who want beautiful wedding stationery that feels personal, polished, and easy to use.</p></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container content"><h2>Our style</h2><p>Our designs blend soft romantic details with warm mid-century modern inspiration. Think clean layouts, vintage-inspired color palettes, playful shapes, and stationery that feels stylish without being overly complicated.</p><h2>What we create</h2><p>We focus on editable wedding invitation suites, bridal shower invitations, wedding menu cards, thank you cards, signage, and printable templates that help bring a celebration together.</p><h2>Why templates?</h2><p>Wedding planning already comes with enough decisions. Editable templates make it easier to create coordinated stationery while still giving you room to personalize the wording, details, and final look.</p></div></section>
  </main>
</Layout>
